productBaseInfoV1.title: Zotac ZBOX-ID86-BE - Intel NM10, Intel Dual Core Atom D2550, DDR3  Barebone Mini PC
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: If you are looking for a computer that is portable, eco-friendly, versatile, stylish and powerful, the Zotac ZBOX-ID86-BE mini-PC is what you seek. Mini-PCs are the next step in the evolution of personal computers and Zotac offers some of the finest mini-PCs around. The compact nature of the Zotac ZBOX-ID86-BE mini-PC allows it to blend right into any room, be it your home or office, without occupying too much space. Extremely light, you can effortlessly carry this mini-PC around and link it to any compatible display screen so as to turn the latter into a makeshift computer - its that easy! Performance The Zotac ZBOX-ID86-BE mini-PC is equipped with an Intel Atom D2550 processor (a dual-core processor that can hit a clock speed of 1.86 GHz) and an Intel NM10 chipset. This mini-PC offers a processor cache of 1 MB. Hence, all the tasks and processes assigned to this computer will be done in a jiffy. Capable of supporting DDR3 RAM of up to 4 GB, the Zotac ZBOX-ID86-BE mini-PC runs on the Windows operating system which makes system navigation a breeze. Furthermore, this mini-PC contains space for a 2.5-inch hard drive disk. Audiovisual Features Boasting a mighty NVIDIA GeForce GT 610 graphics processing unit, the Zotac ZBOX-ID86-BE is able to render impeccably detailed images on the compatible display screen that you have connected it to, hence, your favourite movies, TV shows or video games will come to life on your TV screen or monitor. In addition, the PureVideo HD technology coupled with the HDMI 1.4a feature further enhances the audiovisual capabilities of this mini-PC. Connectivity Convert any room into a media centre by attaching a slew of compatible external device into the USB 3.0 and USB 2.0 ports of the Zotac ZBOX-ID86-BE. There is also a 6-in-1 memory card reader that has been included in this mini-PC. Usage: Firstly, connect the provided adapter to your Intel NUC Kit D34010WYK to power it up. Following this, based on your preferences and requisites, you can connect an external keyboard, mouse and any other compatible device to this mini-PC to fulfill your technological/entertainment-based needs.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Zotac ZBOX-ID18-E - Intel NM70 Express, Intel Processor, DDR3  Barebone Mini PC
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Are you looking for a highly portable and versatile computer that can deliver a powerful performance? Well, the Zotac ZBOX-ID18-E Mini PC is what you seek. Extremely light, this Mini-PC can be effortlessly carried around and all you need to do to utilize it is connect it to a compatible display screen such as a monitor or TV, be it in your house or your office. Energy efficient, the Zotac ZBOX-ID18-E requires very little power to function. Furthermore, you no longer have to be worried about burdening your room space with unnecessary computer-related equipment as this compact PC solves that problem. Performance Comprising of an Intel NM70 Express chipset, a processor cache of 2 MB and an Intel dual-core processor that can hit a clock speed of 1.5 GHz, the Zotac ZBOX-ID18-E can get numerous tasks and processes done in no time. This Mini-PC supports DDR3 RAM of up to 16 GB. You can also connect a 2.5-inch SATA HDD into the provided drive bay. The Zotac ZBOX-ID18-E functions on the Windows operating system, hence, navigating this computer is a breeze. Audiovisual Features Watching movies, TV shows and playing adrenaline-pumping video games have just become more enjoyable and magical as the Zotac ZBOX-ID18-E comes equipped with an Intel HD Graphics graphics processing unit that renders detailed images on the display screen that this Mini-PC is linked to. Furthermore, this Mini-PC delivers stereo sound and you can get an impressive 8-channel surround audio experience by connecting the necessary audio output devices to the provided HDMI port - create an immersive home theatre within the comfort of your house or any place you please. Connectivity Two USB 3.0 ports and four USB 2.0 ports have been built into this Mini-PC to which you can link an array of compatible devices like a keyboard, mouse and much more so as to accomplish all your computer-related needs. Furthermore, the Zotac ZBOX-ID18-E is also endowed with a 6-in-1 card reader. Usage Firstly, connect the provided adapter to your Zotac ZBOX-ID18-E to power it up. Following this, based on your preferences and requisites, you can connect an external keyboard, mouse and any other compatible device to this Mini-PC to fulfill your technological and entertainment-based needs.

productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Looking for a handy, portable media centre? You have just found it. The Zotac ZBOX EI730 Mini-PC is a marvel of modern-day technological ingenuity. Compact, this Mini-PC can be carried around with very little effort and it can be connected to any compatible display screen so as to be used. productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Technological convenience has been redefined now that Zotac has come out with the ZBOX-ID88 Mini PC.
